# Re-run the Playwright QA with CORRECTED criteria:
# - "black sections" are intentional dark theme (rgb(17,17,17), rgb(20,20,20), rgb(10,10,10))
# - The REAL test is: no overflow, scroll stable, sections present, CTAs work, videos have posters
